data.description: 14-acre property in the heart of country living. This 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom, 2349-square-foot home could use some TLC to become a serene and spacious retreat. Built in 1975, the property features a well and septic system, to provide a self-sufficient and sustainable living environment with cross-fenced areas, vegetable gardens, and mature fruit trees. Property also includes a 220v shop and various outbuildings, along with an unfinished basement that has a separate entrance. New roof and gutters Sept 2023.
